 2012-07412012-05-31,  ,  EC,  , 
ActMigratory Birds Convention Act, 1994
SubjectRegulations Amending the Migratory Birds Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the MIGRATORY BIRDS REGULATIONS in order to change hunting season dates, set daily bag limits and possession limits as well as make other related modifications for certain species of migratory game birds for the 2012/2013 hunting season. These amendments will ensure the sustainable harvest of migratory game bird populations.
